content: Search the web to find a list of the most popular ice cream flavors.

I currently don't have real-time internet access to browse the web. However, I can provide you with a list of popular ice cream flavors based on general knowledge up to October 2023:

1. Vanilla
2. Chocolate
3. Strawberry
4. Mint Chocolate Chip
5. Cookies and Cream
6. Rocky Road
7. Butter Pecan
8. Cookie Dough
9. Neapolitan
10. Salted Caramel

These flavors are often favorites in many parts of the world, but popularity can vary by region and individual preference.
